    <title>About this Document</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p id="This_manual_is_an_introductio_concept_conbody_section_p_1"
                    >This document is for internal use only. It gives detailed instructions on how to establish an HTTPS connection between the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> components.</p>
            <p>Starting with <ph conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> V1.1, the HTTPS protocol is supported for communication between the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> Service and the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> Log Agent as well as between the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> Service and the <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> Metrics Agent. </p>
